name: Colours of Your Soul Madame Love

metadata.name: Mystical Magnanimous Madm
metadata.description:
Made with full force love, by Madame Love.

Madm is an incredible force to be reckoned with. She's not afraid to blaze her own path, standing out in her fierce abundance of passion to the point of setting the whole world on fire if need be.

And underneath, is a heart so large and caring that one kiss would melt even the largest of beasts. 

So grateful to have another madame in my life and one who is so inspiring. 

If you like what you see, and want a COLOUR ME! Custom Portrait please reach out to www.madamelove.io.
